1
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:58,160
Short of money.

2
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:02,130
You should have told me if you were short of money.

3
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:07,200
Whenever any of you were in trouble,

4
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,800
wasn't I the one who fixed it?

5
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,720
Which one of you

6
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,640
wasn't painstakingly

7
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,840
trained by me?

8
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:18,280
Taking outside jobs behind the company's back.

9
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,800
Betrayal.

10
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,650
Traitor.

11
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,200
Boss.

12
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,920
Boss.

13
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,680
I know I was wrong.

14
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:28,920
Please spare me this time.

15
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,600
All right.

16
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,440
You say you know,

17
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,920
but I doubt you know it in your heart.

18
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,920
You don't even tell me

19
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,960
what kind of work you do

20
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,160
to make so much money.

21
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,800
You have a way to make money,

22
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,200
and you don't even share it with me.

23
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,720
Brother.

24
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,960
My life is yours.

25
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,800
But for this matter,

26
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,480
for your own good,

27
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,240
I really can't tell you.

28
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,400
Ermao.

29
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,000
He likes money.

30
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,980
Give him a little more.

31
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:08,730
Brother.

32
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,000
The police cars are here.

33
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,440
That guy Sun Xun seems to be there too.

34
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,040
Brother.

35
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,040
How about

36
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,040
I

37
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:14,920
go

38
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,040
hide first.

39
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,720
Hao Weiguo.

40
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,130
Long time no see.

41
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,600
Oh.

42
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,200
What brings

43
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,079
you two here?

44
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,960
Just let me know if you need anything.

45
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,690
I need you to identify someone.

46
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,440
Do you recognize him?

47
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:34,880
Oh.

48
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:38,140
I don't recognize him.

49
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:38,880
Look carefully.

50
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,880
You really don't?

51
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,280
I really don't.

52
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,650
Hey, bro,

53
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,010
do me a favor.

54
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,850
What's wrong, Captain Sun?

55
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,570
Hao Weiguo, take a closer look.

56
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,580
Look familiar?

57
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,360
When was this drawn?

58
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:09,840
This...

59
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,520
Okay, fine.

60
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,980
Don't mess with me.

61
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,140
Don't you recognize your own guy?

62
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,440
Would I lie to you about this?

63
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,279
Take a closer look.

64
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,209
Oh, Captain Sun,

65
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,519
if this was really my guy,

66
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,600
I'd definitely know him at a glance.

67
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,920
Hao Weiguo, let me remind you.

68
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,440
This person is currently suspected of a major criminal case.

69
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,600
If you harbor or cover up for him,

70
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,400
you know the consequences.

71
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,400
Okay, okay, okay.

72
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:31,640
Oh.

73
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:34,120
Boss Hao, you really have a big business.

74
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,980
Throwing money on the ground when you have too much.

75
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,400
Business is good.

76
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,600
Just playing around.

77
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,040
Open it and let me see.

78
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,560
Oh.

79
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,600
Inside here,

80
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:53,480
these brats throw

81
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,600
all sorts of junk.

82
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:55,980
No need to look.

83
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,840
Open it and let me see.

84
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:58,240
Oh.

85
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,640
It's personal privacy.

86
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,840
Open it and let me see.

87
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,040
Don't bother.

88
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,300
We'll do it ourselves.

89
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:45,880
Hao Quezi,

90
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,480
is selling coffins

91
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,760
this profitable now?

92
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,000
You flatter me.

93
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:50,560
Look,

94
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,120
I pray here every day.

95
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,320
Stop.

96
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,480
Stop!

97
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:04,960
Stop.

98
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,930
Split up and search.

99
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,400
Stop.

100
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,000
Still running, you little brat.

101
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,159
Stop.

102
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,200
Don't run.

103
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,730
Are you okay?

104
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,080
He can't get away.

105
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,409
Go find Cripple Hao.

106
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,720
I really don't know what he did.

107
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,880
He arrived just before you did.

108
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,000
He said

109
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,740
he offended some enemies.

110
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,760
He was so scared

111
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,840
that he dove right into the chicken coop.

112
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,360
I was just about to ask him,

113
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,720
when you came.

114
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,920
This kid...

115
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,120
What's his name?

116
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,800
Where does he live?

117
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,400
His name is

118
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,360
Chen Zhao.

119
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,560
He lives in

120
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,440
the old factory area of the chain plant.

121
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:02,960
Hey,

122
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,880
let me ask you something.

123
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,120
What did this kid do?

124
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,200
He's suspected of

125
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,080
a major vicious crime.

126
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,360
Impossible.

127
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,760
Absolutely impossible.

128
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,440
He's just a kid.

129
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,400
Whenever he sees people fighting,

130
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,530
he hides in the back.

131
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,240
I'll vouch for him.

132
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:29,320
Even if he had the guts,

133
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,880
he wouldn't do such a thing.

134
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:32,440
Then help us find him,

135
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,919
and we'll confirm

136
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,780
whether he has the guts or not.

137
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,480
Hao Weiguo,

138
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,880
you can definitely find him.

139
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,860
I'll wait to hear from you.

140
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,330
I'll be waiting.

141
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,770
What should we do, boss?

142
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,520
Tell Xiaozhao to leave immediately.

143
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,400
As far away as possible.

144
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,560
But boss,

145
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:09,720
what Xiaozhao did...

146
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,920
Then we really can't let him get caught.

147
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,340
Think about it.

148
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,680
If we catch him,

149
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,520
the money becomes stolen goods.

150
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,840
We won't get a single cent.

151
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,640
It might even implicate us.

152
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,720
Are you covering for him?

153
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,000
Chen Zhao.

154
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,180
Damn it.

155
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,050
Every lead we follow goes cold.

156
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,620
We're just so unlucky.

157
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,120
Tell me,

158
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,840
Chen Zhao fled from Hao Weiguo's place,

159
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,200
and is his lackey.

160
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,320
This must have something

161
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,920
to do with Hao Weiguo, right?

162
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,200
So the lead on Hao the Cripple

163
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,320
must not be dropped.

164
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,380
Keep tracking him.

165
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:55,840
Sir.

166
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,570
How did it go?

167
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,440
We found this in Chen Zhao's house.

168
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,970
He's been watching Zhang Biao for a long time.

169
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,520
This guy is so distracted while tailing.

170
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,920
He's even taking pictures of pretty girls.

171
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,760
Hey, isn't this Qiao Sisi?

172
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,800
Why is he tailing her?

173
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,520
What's the relationship between them?

174
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:26,770
Don't worry.

175
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,120
Once Chen Zhao is found,

176
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,280
everything will be clear.

177
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,560
You must all be exhausted lately.

178
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,560
Take shifts to get some rest.

179
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:31,960
Go on.

180
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,170
Thank you, Captain.

181
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,640
Let's go, Lao Yan.

182
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,280
I'll treat you to

183
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,540
a meal at Old Han's.

184
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,540
I'm not hungry.

185
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,560
Mr. Han texted me.

186
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,200
Guannan is there.

187
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,340
The girl from the Zhang family

188
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,680
is so beautiful.

189
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,480
Uncle Han.

190
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,080
The usual.

191
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:05,960
Got it.

192
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,160
Guannan.

193
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,120
Xun.

194
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,040
It's been a long time.

195
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,040
I've been so busy lately.

196
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,300
We didn't even have time to eat together.

197
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,240
Guannan.

198
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:24,450
Sit down.

199
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,160
Just like before,

200
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,420
let's have a good meal.

201
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,240
A toast to the two great detectives

202
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,640
for finally solving the private room case.

203
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,500
Brother Mi.

204
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,760
Tell me.

205
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,650
How did you two find the killer?

206
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,960
Let's see if it's like in the movies.

207
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,610
Our police force has rules.

208
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,280
We can't leak case secrets.

209
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,600
Unless you also go to the police academy and become a cop

210
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,360
to join us.

211
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,240
Oh.

212
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,480
No way.

213
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,760
I want to be an actor,

214
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,720
a performing artist.

215
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,480
Do you think it's that easy to be a performing artist?

216
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,120
Then

217
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:14,160
I just need to work harder, right?

218
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:16,020
What if I actually make it one day?

219
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,840
Do you want my autograph now?

220
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:21,680
It'll be priceless once I'm famous.

221
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,080
You guys don't want it?

222
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,040
You don't want it, right?

223
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:26,040
I'll take it then.

224
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,340
Sign one for me.

225
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,880
It has to be my brother Xun.

226
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:29,860
Right here.

227
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,620
Signing again.

228
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,760
This is already

229
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:35,090
the 27th autograph you've signed for him.

230
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,080
Tch.

231
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,400
You don't understand.

232
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,450
Guannan.

233
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,840
How long has it been since the three of us

234
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,400
had a meal together?

235
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:00,960
Sit down.

236
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,170
It's different now.

237
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,240
Some people

238
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,520
will never be able to eat here again.

239
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:32,690
Guannan.

240
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:34,890
Guannan.

241
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:37,760
It's been five years.

242
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:41,440
I thought we could sit together and have a meal.

243
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,680
I just want to tell you,

244
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,720
I have never let go of Master's case.

245
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:49,320
I will definitely clear up all the doubts.

246
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,760
Yan.

247
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:50,960
Stop talking.

248
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:00,800
Okay.

249
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,080
Then tell me,

250
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,940
what exactly are you suspecting?

251
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:08,640
Suspecting that Ma Guangfu was ordered to plant the bomb?

252
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:11,340
Suspecting that my dad was their target?

253
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,120
When you figure it out,

254
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:15,120
will time go back to five years ago?

255
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:17,520
Will my dad come back to life?

256
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:22,240
Will this ruined skin and flesh on my body heal?

257
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,000
I hate you.

258
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,760
The person he wanted to take revenge on was clearly you,

259
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:29,880
but you had to act eager and lend the car to my dad.

260
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,800
I also know it wasn't your fault.

261
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,120
But you stand here alive,

262
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:38,450
and say over and over that you want to clear up all the doubts.

263
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,280
It's been five years.

264
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,520
Any results?

265
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,840
Every day you pretend you want to find the truth,

266
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,480
but deep down you know better than anyone

267
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:52,920
that your so-called doubts and truth

268
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:55,760
are just an excuse to shift your guilt.

269
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,720
The killer committed suicide to escape punishment.

270
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,560
This answer is too simple, isn't it?

271
00:14:59,560 --> 00:15:02,400
Too simple to hold your guilt and pain.

272
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:05,520
So you endlessly try to prove there's another killer.

273
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,920
Actually, you just want to find a scapegoat

274
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:09,600
to make yourself feel better

275
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:12,200
and escape your own guilt.

276
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,680
Every time you bring up the past,

277
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:16,560
it's like adding another scar to my rotting flesh.

278
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,280
You are not investigating a case.

279
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:21,000
You are clearly using my pain

280
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,160
to feed your pitiful guilt.

281
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:24,760
Yan Mi.

282
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:26,120
Please stop acting like

283
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,440
the whole world doesn't understand you

284
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,880
and you're the only one carrying the truth.

285
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,280
It's really ridiculous.

286
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:34,120
If nobody is wrong,

287
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,320
then who is?

288
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,600
Me?

289
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,320
I harmed you and Master.

290
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,580
Nothing I say matters.

291
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,120
But I believe

292
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:47,240
Master wants me to find out the truth.

293
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,080
Whatever.

294
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:49,160
Han.

295
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,060
Check, please.

296
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:52,040
I'm done.

297
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,400
Han,

298
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,500
put it on my tab.

299
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,280
Sure.

300
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,980
I still have my hands and feet.

301
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:07,480
I can make money

302
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,320
and afford to eat.

303
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,080
Treat them.

304
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:16,970
No...

305
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:19,960
Guannan.

306
00:16:22,400 --> 00:16:23,130
Captain Sun.

307
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:23,560
Here.

308
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,120
Here, Xiaoyan.

309
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:28,840
Xiaoyan,

310
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:29,600
yours.

311
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:31,240
Mildly numb and spicy.

312
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,040
Captain Sun's,

313
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,280
insanely spicy.

314
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,440
Sit down and eat.

315
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,160
Okay.

316
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,280
Thanks, Han.

317
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,440
Okay.

318
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,560
Where does Guannan live now?

319
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,740
He sold the old house in the family compound.

320
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:01,160
Now he's moved to a

321
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,320
bachelor apartment.

322
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,180
I went to see it.

323
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,280
The conditions are pretty good.

324
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,200
It's for the best.

325
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,280
If he stayed in the old house,

326
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,960
thinking about the past every day,

327
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,619
it'd be hard for him to move on.

328
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,640
What Guannan said

329
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:15,839
was just him venting.

330
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,440
For so many years,

331
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:18,880
no one

332
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,260
could really help him.

333
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:41,960
I've worried so much about you two.

334
00:17:58,840 --> 00:17:59,240
Hello?

335
00:18:05,320 --> 00:18:05,760
Okay.

336
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:06,480
Got it.

337
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,000
Let's go.

338
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,130
Back to the station.

339
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,240
Ma Jinguang confessed.
